<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Indufrial | Executive Decision Board</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#050c16;
      --bg2:#0a1422;
      --panel:#0d1828;
      --panel-2:#101f34;
      --stroke:rgba(124,156,205,.18);
      --stroke-strong:rgba(113,184,255,.42);
      --text:#edf4ff;
      --muted:#92a7c9;
      --blue:#5aa2ff;
      --cyan:#66ddff;
      --amber:#fbb86d;
      --green:#57d6a0;
      --shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.42);
      --radius:26px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 8% 10%, rgba(90,162,255,.16), transparent 20%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 8%, rgba(102,221,255,.12), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 100%, rgba(251,184,109,.06), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #040a13 0%, #07111d 100%);
      scroll-behavior:smooth;
    }

    .wrap{
      width:min(1280px, calc(100% - 28px));
      margin:0 auto;
    }

    .topbar{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      background:rgba(5,12,22,.68);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    }

    .topbar-inner{
      min-height:72px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:16px;
    }

    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:14px;
      min-width:0;
    }

    .logo{
      width:44px;
      height:44px;
      border-radius:14px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      font-weight:900;
      color:#fff;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d4ed8,#2563eb 58%, #38bdf8);
      box-shadow:0 14px 30px rgba(37,99,235,.35);
      flex-shrink:0;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      font-size:11px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.28em;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:4px;
      white-space:nowrap;
    }

    .title-sm{
      font-size:14px;
      font-weight:900;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      white-space:nowrap;
      overflow:hidden;
      text-overflow:ellipsis;
    }

    .hero{
      padding:34px 0 20px;
    }

    .hero-shell{
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
      border-radius:34px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15,26,43,.96), rgba(8,15,28,.96));
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-shell::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, rgba(255,255,255,.03) 50%, transparent 100%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .hero-grid{
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;
      gap:0;
    }

    .hero-left{
      padding:34px 30px 30px;
      border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    }

    .hero-right{
      padding:24px;
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
      align-content:start;
    }

    .hero-badge{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.035);
      color:#c8daf8;
      font-size:11px;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.22em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    h1{
      margin:18px 0 0;
      font-size:clamp(38px,6vw,78px);
      line-height:.92;
      letter-spacing:-.055em;
      font-weight:900;
      max-width:11ch;
    }

    .lead{
      margin:18px 0 0;
      max-width:58ch;
      color:#c2d2ea;
      line-height:1.65;
      font-size:clamp(15px,2vw,18px);
    }

    .hero-stats{
      margin-top:24px;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:14px;
    }

    .stat{
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:16px;
    }

    .stat-k{
      font-size:10px;
      letter-spacing:.24em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .stat-v{
      font-size:16px;
      font-weight:800;
      line-height:1.3;
    }

    .signal{
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.028);
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:18px;
    }

    .signal-k{
      font-size:10px;
      letter-spacing:.24em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#8db7ff;
      font-weight:800;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .signal-v{
      margin:0;
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.55;
      color:#e7f0ff;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .section{
      padding:18px 0 30px;
    }

    .board-shell{
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
      border-radius:34px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13,24,40,.96), rgba(8,14,24,.96));
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      padding:24px;
    }

    .board-shell::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0 88%, rgba(255,255,255,.02) 100%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .board-head{
      display:flex;
      align-items:end;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:18px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-bottom:22px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:2;
    }

    .board-title{
      margin:0;
      font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);
      line-height:1;
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
      font-weight:900;
    }

    .board-sub{
      margin:10px 0 0;
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:68ch;
      line-height:1.6;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .board-note{
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius:16px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      color:#dbe9ff;
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.16em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .flow-area{
      position:relative;
      padding:8px 0 4px;
    }

    .flow-lines{
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      pointer-events:none;
      opacity:.95;
    }

    .board-grid{
      position:relative;
      z-index:2;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(12, 1fr);
      gap:16px;
      align-items:stretch;
    }

    .module{
      position:relative;
      min-height:168px;
      border-radius:28px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.045), rgba(255,255,255,.022));
      cursor:pointer;
      overflow:hidden;
      transition:transform .22s ease, border-color .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease, background .22s ease;
      box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(0,0,0,.18);
      isolation:isolate;
    }

    .module::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:auto -10% -20% auto;
      width:130px;
      height:130px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(90,162,255,.16), transparent 68%);
      z-index:-1;
    }

    .module::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.04), transparent 46%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .module:hover,
    .module.active{
      transform:translateY(-4px);
      border-color:var(--stroke-strong);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18,35,60,.82), rgba(12,24,42,.82));
      box-shadow:0 18px 42px rgba(2,8,18,.44);
    }

    .module-inner{
      height:100%;
      padding:18px 18px 16px;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:14px;
    }

    .module-top{
      display:flex;
      align-items:flex-start;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:10px;
    }

    .n{
      width:46px;
      height:46px;
      border-radius:16px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      font-size:16px;
      font-weight:900;
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(18,35,60,.28);
    }

    .micro{
      font-size:10px;
      letter-spacing:.22em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-weight:800;
      margin-top:4px;
      text-align:right;
    }

    .module h3{
      margin:0;
      font-size:20px;
      line-height:1.04;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
      font-weight:900;
      max-width:12ch;
    }

    .module p{
      margin:0;
      color:#c0d0e9;
      font-size:14px;
      line-height:1.52;
    }

    .m1,.m2,.m3,.m4,.m5,.m6,.m7,.m8,.m9,.m10,.m11{grid-column:span 4;}
    .m1 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#38bdf8)}
    .m2 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0ea5e9,#06b6d4)}
    .m3 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#60a5fa)}
    .m4 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#64748b,#334155)}
    .m5 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f766e,#10b981)}
    .m6 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d97706,#f59e0b)}
    .m7 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0ea5e9,#2563eb)}
    .m8 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#059669,#34d399)}
    .m9 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ea580c,#fb923c)}
    .m10 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#1d4ed8)}
    .m11 .n{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#22c55e,#16a34a)}

    .detail-shell{
      margin-top:18px;
      overflow:hidden;
      border-radius:34px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13,24,40,.98), rgba(8,14,24,.98));
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .detail-top{
      padding:22px 22px 0;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:14px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .detail-badge{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.035);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      color:#d9e7fd;
      font-size:11px;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.18em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    .detail-actions{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .btn{
      appearance:none;
      border:none;
      cursor:pointer;
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:13px 16px;
      font:inherit;
      font-weight:800;
      transition:transform .18s ease, background .18s ease, border-color .18s ease, opacity .18s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px)}
    .btn-primary{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#38bdf8);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 14px 26px rgba(37,99,235,.3);
    }

    .btn-secondary{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      color:#d9e8ff;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }

    .detail-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.03fr .97fr;
      gap:18px;
      padding:20px 22px 22px;
    }

    .detail-card{
      border-radius:28px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.028);
      padding:22px;
      min-height:100%;
    }

    .detail-card h2{
      margin:0 0 10px;
      font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);
      line-height:.96;
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
      font-weight:900;
      max-width:14ch;
    }

    .detail-card p{
      margin:0;
      color:#c7d7ee;
      line-height:1.66;
      font-size:15px;
    }

    .meta{
      margin-top:18px;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
      gap:12px;
    }

    .meta-box{
      padding:16px;
      border-radius:20px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.025);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
    }

    .meta-k{
      margin:0 0 7px;
      font-size:10px;
      letter-spacing:.22em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .meta-v{
      margin:0;
      font-weight:800;
      line-height:1.48;
      color:#eef5ff;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .detail-list{
      display:grid;
      gap:12px;
    }

    .detail-item{
      border-radius:22px;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.025);
      padding:16px;
    }

    .detail-item .k{
      margin:0 0 8px;
      font-size:10px;
      letter-spacing:.22em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      font-weight:800;
      color:#8db7ff;
    }

    .detail-item .v{
      margin:0;
      color:#ebf3ff;
      font-weight:700;
      line-height:1.55;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    .footer{
      padding:18px 0 34px;
      text-align:center;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:.16em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px){
      .hero-grid,
      .detail-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .hero-left{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
      .m1,.m2,.m3,.m4,.m5,.m6,.m7,.m8,.m9,.m10,.m11{grid-column:span 6;}
      .flow-lines{display:none}
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px){
      .wrap{width:min(100% - 18px, 1280px)}
      .topbar-inner{min-height:66px}
      .hero-left,.hero-right,.board-shell,.detail-top,.detail-grid{padding-left:16px;padding-right:16px}
      .hero-shell,.board-shell,.detail-shell{border-radius:24px}
      .hero-stats{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .board-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:12px}
      .m1,.m2,.m3,.m4,.m5,.m6,.m7,.m8,.m9,.m10,.m11{grid-column:auto}
      .module{min-height:144px;border-radius:24px}
      .module h3{font-size:18px;max-width:none}
      .detail-card{padding:18px}
      .meta{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .btn{width:100%}
      .detail-actions{width:100%}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="wrap topbar-inner">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="logo">I</div>
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Executive Decision Board</div>
          <div class="title-sm">Indufrial · Canal comercial digital</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="wrap hero-shell">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <section class="hero-left">
          <div class="hero-badge">Arquitectura ejecutiva de decisión</div>
          <h1>Lo que presidencia necesita ver para decidir.</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Este tablero responde, en una sola estructura visual, las preguntas críticas sobre creación, alcance, tiempos, riesgo, minivictorias y arranque del canal comercial digital de Indufrial.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-k">Frentes de avance</div>
              <div class="stat-v">6 frentes iniciales</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-k">Hitos de control</div>
              <div class="stat-v">4 hitos verificables</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-k">Resultado esperado</div>
              <div class="stat-v">Base real para arrancar</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <aside class="hero-right">
          <div class="signal">
            <div class="signal-k">Qué resuelve</div>
            <p class="signal-v">Cómo crear correctamente el canal desde cero, sin que nazca con vacíos operativos ni desorden interno.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="signal">
            <div class="signal-k">Qué deja instalado</div>
            <p class="signal-v">Una base estructurada de implementación, criterios de control y activación del primer frente de ejecución.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="signal">
            <div class="signal-k">Cómo se usa</div>
            <p class="signal-v">Toque cualquier módulo. El panel inferior abre la respuesta ejecutiva concreta para esa duda de presidencia.</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <section class="board-shell">
        <div class="board-head">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Decision architecture</div>
            <h2 class="board-title">11 preguntas críticas que este tablero debe resolver</h2>
            <p class="board-sub">
              Cada módulo responde una duda concreta sobre valor, método, recorrido, tiempo, minivictorias, velocidad, riesgo y condiciones de arranque.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="board-note">Toque un módulo</div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-area">
          <svg class="flow-lines" viewBox="0 0 1200 760" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M190 95 C 285 95, 285 95, 380 95" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M590 95 C 685 95, 685 95, 780 95" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>

            <path d="M980 150 C 980 205, 980 205, 980 260" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M780 315 C 685 315, 685 315, 590 315" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M380 315 C 285 315, 285 315, 190 315" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>

            <path d="M190 370 C 190 425, 190 425, 190 480" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M190 535 C 285 535, 285 535, 380 535" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M590 535 C 685 535, 685 535, 780 535" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>

            <path d="M980 590 C 980 645, 980 645, 980 700" stroke="rgba(102,221,255,.16)" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>

            <circle cx="380" cy="95" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
            <circle cx="780" cy="95" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
            <circle cx="980" cy="260" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
            <circle cx="590" cy="315" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
            <circle cx="190" cy="315" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
            <circle cx="190" cy="480" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
            <circle cx="380" cy="535" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
            <circle cx="780" cy="535" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
            <circle cx="980" cy="700" r="5" fill="rgba(90,162,255,.55)"/>
          </svg>

          <div class="board-grid" id="boardGrid">
            <article class="module m1 active" data-id="1">
              <div class="module-inner">
                <div>
                  <div class="module-top">
                    <div class="n">01</div>
                    <div class="micro">Problema</div>
                  </div>
                  <h3>¿Qué problema real resuelve?</h3>
                </div>
                <p>Crear correctamente el canal desde cero, sin improvisación operativa.</p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="module m2" data-id="2">
              <div class="module-inner">
                <div>
                  <div class="module-top">
                    <div class="n">02</div>
                    <div class="micro">Momento</div>
                  </div>
                  <h3>¿Por qué vale la pena hacerlo ahora?</h3>
                </div>
                <p>La oportunidad existe hoy, pero necesita estructura antes de moverse.</p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="module m3" data-id="3">
              <div class="module-inner">
                <div>
                  <div class="module-top">
                    <div class="n">03</div>
                    <div class="micro">Entrega</div>
                  </div>
                  <h3>¿Qué va a entregar exactamente?</h3>
                </div>
                <p>Una base real de arranque, control y activación inicial.</p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="module m4" data-id="4">
              <div class="module-inner">
                <div>
                  <div class="module-top">
                    <div class="n">04</div>
                    <div class="micro">Método</div>
                  </div>
                  <h3>¿Qué va a hacer y cómo?</h3>
                </div>
                <p>Estructurar el canal paso a paso bajo lógica de implementación.</p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="module m5" data-id="5">
              <div class="module-inner">
                <div>
                  <div class="module-top">
                    <div class="n">05</div>
